    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Lifestyle Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Department Manager to strengthen our Jabalpur-based team.\n\nAbout Lifestyle Advisory Limited:\nLifestyle Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Lifestyle Advisory Limited!",
